        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 47. Living snails from Bau A Cyclophorus perdix borneensis (Metcalfe, 1851) ME 8753 Gunung Kapor B Platyrhaphe linita (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 9700 Gunung Doya C Stomacosmethis sadongensis (E. A. Smith, 1895) ME 8761 Gunung Kapor D Pincerna globosa (H. Adams, 1870) ME 8749 Lobang Angin. All not to scale." , "Figure 7. A Opisthophorus biciliatus (Mousson, 1849) ME 8754 Gunung Kapor B Opisthophorus birostris (L. Pfeiffer, 1854) ME 8758 Gunung Kapor C Opisthophorus cavernae (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 8904 Gunung Doya D Opisthophorus euryomphalus (L. Pfeiffer, 1856) ME 8779 Gunung Kapor E Platyrhaphe linita (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 0881 Gunung Batu F Pterocyclos tenuilabiatus (Metcalfe, 1851) ME 5910 Gunung Batu." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536835" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/536795" .

